      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, showroom-quality condition, meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards. The exterior is flawless, featuring a factory-fresh paint finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in 'like-new' state, with premium materials that show no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a collector or a buyer seeking a truly mint-condition vehicle.",
